ss=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat.succ\">succ</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">j</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Uncontracted.html#WickContraction.uncontracted\">uncontracted</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a Wick contraction `φsΛ` associated with a list of states `φs`\nand an `i : Fin φs.length.succ`, the change in sign of the contraction associated with\ninserting `φ` into `φs` at position `i` and contracting it with `j : c.uncontracted`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/InsertSome.html#WickContraction.signInsertSome","kind":"def","line":239,"name":"WickContraction.signInsertSome","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L239-L244"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/InsertSome.html#WickContraction.signInsertSomeCoef\"><span class=\"name\">WickContraction</span>.<span class=\"name\">signInsertSomeCoef</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification\">FieldSpecification</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φs</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓕</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/FieldSpecification/Basic.html#FieldSpecification.FieldOp\">FieldOp</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Basic.html#WickContraction\">WickContraction</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Fin\">Fin</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φs</span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List.length\">length</a></span>.<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat.succ\">succ</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">j</span> : <span class=\"fn\">↥<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">φsΛ</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Uncontracted.html#WickContraction.uncontracted\">uncontracted</a></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Complex/Basic.html#Complex\">ℂ</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a Wick contraction `φsΛ` the sign defined in the following way,\nrelated to inserting a field `φ` at position `i` and contracting it with `j : φsΛ.uncontracted`.\n- If `j < i`, for each field `φₐ` in `φⱼ₊₁…φᵢ₋₁` without a dual at position `< j`\n  the sign `𝓢(φₐ, φᵢ)`.\n- Else, for each field `φₐ` in `φᵢ…φⱼ₋₁` of `φs` without dual at position `< i` the sign\n  `𝓢(φₐ, φⱼ)`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/QFT/PerturbationTheory/WickContraction/Sign/InsertSome.html#WickContraction.signInsertSomeCoef","kind":"def","line":224,"name":"WickContraction.signInsertSomeCoef","